msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "NEC - PC Engine / SuperGrafx / CD (Beetle PCE)"
msgstr "NEC — PC Engine / SuperGrafx / CD (Beetle PCE)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Beetle PC Engine is a fork of Mednafen's PC Engine driver.[CR][CR]This PC Engine module is more accurate than the Beetle PC Engine Fast module, at the expense of speed."
msgstr "Beetle PC Engine — это форк драйвера PC Engine от Mednafen.[CR][CR]Этот модуль PC Engine более точен, чем модуль Beetle PC Engine Fast, но за счёт скорости."

